      • PropertyType

        public PropertyType(String id,
            int position,
            String displayName,
            LogicalType logicalType,
            boolean isMandatory)
        Constructs a new PropertyType by initializing all mandatory fields.
        Parameters:
        id - A String containing the identifier of this PropertyType.
        position - The position of this PropertyType within its ItemType.
        displayName - A String containing the human-readable name of this PropertyType.
        logicalType - The LogicalType of the values of Propertys with this PropertyType.
        isMandatory - true if this PropertyType is mandatory; false otherwise.
